		<RichText x="738" y="479" width="423" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">旋锯飞叶扔出钩锁，并立即驾着飞锯冲来，后接一段划击，两段攻击均造成<span color="#99ff86">80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="703" width="424" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">旋锯飞叶驱使灵力，使用飞锯进行两段旋舞攻击，均造成<span color="#99ff86">80%</span><span>伤害，后飞出锯片并收回，飞出与收回均造成</span><span color="#99ff86">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/匿叶龙武士%B7旋锯飞叶.assets/Image_13.png')" x="718" y="393">
