		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#389a3e" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#389a3e">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="255" width="431" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">旋锯飞叶使用飞锯进行2种至多2段的攻击：<span color="#ceffbf">横纵混合</span><span>，均造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">60%</span><span>伤害；</span><span color="#ceffbf">横纵接锯</span><span>，分别造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">60%,70%</span><span>伤害，且留在地上的锯子额外造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">10%x3</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
